Parameter:
  (<Article number/'followed-up'/'last'>)  

Description:
  Writes a follow-up to the given article. If the article is a usenet
  news, a follow-up news is posted.

  If 'followed-up' is supplied, you write a follow-up to the article 
  last read article was a follow-up to.

  If 'last' is supplied, the follow-up is written to the article last read
  with '(Display) next article' or '(Display) next follow-up'.

  If no article number is supplied, the last read article is followed-up.
